Package: spacexr
Type: Package
Title: SpatialeXpressionR: Cell type identification and cell type-specific differential expression in spatial transcriptomics
Version: 2.2.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dylan", "Cable", email = "dmcable@umich.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Gabriel", "Grajeda", email = "gabriel.grajeda@gmail.com", role = "cre", comment=c(ORCID="0009-0003-7242-7476")))
Description: Implementation of two computational methods in spatial transcriptomics: 
    1. Robust Cell Type Decomposition (RCTD). Decomposes cell type mixtures using cell type profiles, correcting for differences across sequencing technologies.
    2. Cell Type-Specific Inference of Differential Expression (CSIDE). Identifies cell type-specific differential expression, accounting for localization of other cell types.
URL: https://github.com/ggrajeda/spacexr
BugReports: https://github.com/ggrajeda/spacexr/issues
